The Audio Commons Ontology

Description

The Audio Commons Ontology provides main concepts and properties for describing audio content, both musical and non-musical, on the Semantic Web.

Classes: Analog signal, Digital signal, Audio category, Audio clip, Audio manifestation, Audio collection, First node, Node, Last node, Any node but the first, Any node but the last, Audio expression, Audio file, Audio item, Audio publication, Signal, Recording, Signal production, Physical sound, Syntesis.

Object Properties: node content, is in audio category, available as, compiled, encodes, first node, member node, homepage, image, last node, next node, previous node, produced signal, production from, publication of, published, published audio manifestation, recording of.

Datatype Properties: bits per sample, channels, duration, node index, sample rate.

Classes

Analog signal
ac:AnalogSignal

Sub-Classes: mo:AnalogSignal.

Digital signal
ac:DigitalSignal

Super-Classes: Signal. Sub-Classes: mo:DigitalSignal. Domain of: bits per sample, channels, sample rate. Range of: encodes.

Audio category
ac:AudioCategory

Super-Classes: frbr:Concept. Sub-Classes: ac:Instrument, mo:Genre. Range of: is in audio category.

Audio clip
ac:AudioClip

Super-Classes: Audio manifestation. Sub-Classes: mo:Track.

Audio manifestation
ac:AudioManifestation

Super-Classes: cc:Work, frbr:Manifestation. Sub-Classes: Audio clip, Audio collection, mo:MusicalManifestation. Domain of: available as, publication of. Range of: node content, compiled, published, published audio manifestation.

Audio collection
ac:AudioCollection

Super-Classes: Audio manifestation. Sub-Classes: mo:Record, mo:Release. Domain of: first node, member node, last node.

First node
ac:AudioCollectionFirstNode

Super-Classes: Node. Range of: first node.

Node
ac:AudioCollectionNode

Super-Classes: rdf:List, _:b4, _:b5, _:b6. Sub-Classes: First node, Last node, Any node but the first, Any node but the last. Domain of: node content, node index. Range of: member node.

Last node
ac:AudioCollectionLastNode

Super-Classes: Node. Range of: last node.

Any node but the first
ac:AudioCollectionNonFirstNode

Super-Classes: Node. Domain of: previous node. Range of: next node.

Any node but the last
ac:AudioCollectionNonLastNode

Super-Classes: Node. Domain of: next node. Range of: previous node.

Audio expression
ac:AudioExpression

Super-Classes: frbr:Expression. Sub-Classes: Signal, Physical sound, mo:MusicalExpression. Range of: publication of.

Audio file
ac:AudioFile

Super-Classes: ebu:MediaResource, Audio item. Sub-Classes: mo:AudioFile.

Audio item
ac:AudioItem

Super-Classes: frbr:Item. Sub-Classes: Audio file, mo:MusicalItem. Domain of: encodes. Range of: available as.

Audio publication
ac:AudioPublication

Super-Classes: event:Event. Sub-Classes: mo:ReleaseEvent. Domain of: published audio manifestation.

Signal
ac:Signal

Super-Classes: Audio expression. Sub-Classes: Digital signal, mo:Signal. Range of: produced signal.

Recording
ac:Recording

Super-Classes: Signal production. Sub-Classes: mo:Recording. Domain of: recording of.

Signal production
ac:SignalProduction

Super-Classes: event:Event. Sub-Classes: Recording, Syntesis. Domain of: produced signal, production from.

Physical sound
ac:Sound

Super-Classes: Audio expression. Sub-Classes: mo:Sound. Range of: production from, recording of.

Syntesis
ac:Syntesis

Super-Classes: Signal production.
